headline: Wells Fargo sues JPMorgan over troubled $481 million real estate loan
summary: Wells Fargo sued JPMorgan Chase on Monday to recover losses for investors in a $481 million commercial real estate loan that was allegedly based on a fraudulently inflated financial metric.
